ce:ConstraintConcept rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ce#DataAbstraction
ce:DataAbstraction rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ce#DeclarativeParadigm
ce:DeclarativeParadigm rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ce#FM
ce:FM rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ce#GrammarConcept
ce:GrammarConcept rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ce#Grammarware
ce:Grammarware rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ce#Graphware
ce:Graphware rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


