ce:Lists rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ce#LogicParadigm
ce:LogicParadigm rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ce#MDE
ce:MDE rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ce#Markupware
ce:Markupware rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ce#ModelingConcept
ce:ModelingConcept rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/ce#Modelware
ce:Modelware rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


